        <text>
          <![CDATA[ <p><strong>Thirty-Two Hour Workweek Act</strong></p> <p>This bill shortens the standard workweek under federal law from 40 hours to 32 hours over a three-year phase in period. It also requires specified overtime pay for workdays longer than eight hours.</p>]]>
        </text>
